item.title: 15 Hottest Female Soccer Players On The Planet
item.description: Once seen as a male-dominated sport, female soccer players all over the globe are dominating both on and off the field. From their killer looks to their outrageous athletic ability, here are 15 of the most gorgeous and impressive women in soccer. Read on to see if your favorite made the list. England’s Toni Duggan Twitter Toni Duggan celebrated her 18 birthday by scoring the opening goal in England’s 2009 UEFA Women’s Under-19 Championship final win against Sweden in Belarus.
